":"2018-06-10T17:35:19.000Z","msg":"以前ex夾硬幫我掹痛撚到仆街 之後久而久之上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家我去到啲新地方都會掹啲鬚掉落地下 諗住留低足跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576def5e4ba01c3fcd2c8e1467c8be6070b6bc75","tid":696793,"uid":3588,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:36:25.000Z","msg":"原來都會有人抆鬚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次嚮屋企睇電影，一路睇一路抆，睇完成套戲屌佢老尾淨係抆左上唇左邊戈part，因為抆慣左呢個過程太自然，應該話有手癮就抆，有野做就放低左唔會再抆<br />\n我唔記得左自己抆左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後出街同朋友食飯比人笑到顛，問我做咩少左一忽鬚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自此之後剩係成日無野做先夠膽放肆抆鬚，平時要就住就住，好壓抑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6463b6cd56e5ae931b018d1f00817294562f0ee2","tid":696793,"uid":161918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:42:23.000Z","msg":"拔幾條就得<br />\n<br />\n拔得多好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6a4b2778ff9ecb279468ac033853b9ab5833b6","tid":696793,"uid":14820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:45:22.000Z","msg":"感覺啲鬚唔係身體一部分咁<br />\n生出嚟嗰段時間好難頂<br />\n好想掹走佢但又唔夠長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662bba2642a95efd209cdb04900a512d94b8fe9a","tid":696793,"uid":40496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:48:35.000Z","msg":"我抆完好易出暗瘡<br />\n但又停唔到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67315a498334aedc78016fda01b9a0284eccef61","